@startuml
title FastBite MVP - Canais Realtime e Autorizacao
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
left to right direction

actor Customer
actor "Restaurant Staff" as Staff
actor Courier

rectangle "Reverb Channels" {
  rectangle "customer.{customerId}.orders" as CChan
  rectangle "restaurant.{restaurantId}.orders" as RChan
  rectangle "courier.{courierId}.jobs" as JChan
  rectangle "order.{orderId}.tracking" as TChan
}

Customer --> CChan : subscribe own only
Customer --> TChan : subscribe own order only

Staff --> RChan : subscribe own restaurant only
Staff --> TChan : subscribe orders from own restaurant

Courier --> JChan : subscribe own only
Courier --> TChan : subscribe assigned orders only

note bottom of CChan
Events:
- ORDER_*
- PAYMENT_*
end note

note bottom of RChan
Events:
- ORDER_CREATED
- ORDER_CONFIRMED
- ORDER_REJECTED
- ORDER_READY
end note

note bottom of JChan
Events:
- JOB_OFFERED
- JOB_EXPIRED
- JOB_ACCEPTED
end note

note bottom of TChan
Events:
- ORDER_PREPARING
- ORDER_READY
- ORDER_OUT_FOR_DELIVERY
- COURIER_POSITION_UPDATED
- ORDER_DELIVERED
end note

@enduml
